data.description: Very nice move in ready 3 bed 2 bath Ranch with new laminate flooring in the bedrooms. Great kitchen with lots of beautiful cabinetry, large pantry, and all appliances to stay, most around 2 years old. Large living room features laminate floors. The spacious primary bedroom features, crown molding, walk-in closet and full bath. Large garage with tall ceiling height and pull down stairs. Plenty of storage space and appealing decor, round out this wonderful home! Nice size, level fenced back yard, perfect for entertaining or relaxing. This home is conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, major manufacturing and I75.
